    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "devcontainers/ci",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "A GitHub Action and Azure DevOps Task designed to simplify using Dev Containers (https://containers.dev) in CI/CD systems."
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "devcontainers/ci",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "The Dev Container Build and Run GitHub Action is aimed at making it easier to re-use [Dev Containers](https://containers.dev) in a GitHub workflow. The Action supports using a Dev Container to run commands for CI, testing, and more, along with pre-building a Dev Container image.\u2026"
    },
    {
